{"id":27763,"date":"2023-10-14T11:34:05","date_gmt":"2023-10-14T11:34:05","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/wappier.com\/?p=27763"},"modified":"2023-10-18T09:22:18","modified_gmt":"2023-10-18T09:22:18","slug":"price-optimization-tools","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/wappier.com\/price-optimization-tools\/","title":{"rendered":"7 Price Optimization Tools for Driving Sales Lift"},"content":{"rendered":"\t\t<div data-elementor-type=\"wp-post\" data-elementor-id=\"27763\" class=\"elementor elementor-27763\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-section-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-141ffe1 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"141ffe1\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-e0362c6\" data-id=\"e0362c6\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b5351eb elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"b5351eb\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<p>When it comes to performance metrics, incremental lift is often considered by many to be the key to the kingdom.<\/p><p>The ability to prove the effectiveness of a specific promotion can earn marketing and advertising teams access to increased budgets, greater resources, or decision making power within their organizations. But one of the deciding factors in lift is promotional pricing, and offering the right price at the right time requires dedicated analysis of huge quantities of data from a variety of sources. That\u2019s where price optimization tools and software come into play; here\u2019s how price optimization works to drive lift and a look at seven solutions companies can consider.<\/p><p><em><strong>Jump to a section\u2026<\/strong><\/em><\/p><p><strong><a href=\"#sales\">What Is Sales Lift?<\/a><\/strong><\/p><p><strong><a href=\"#lift\">Why Is Sales Lift Important?<\/a><\/strong><\/p><p><strong><a href=\"#play\">What Role Does Price Optimization Play In Sales Lift?<\/a><\/strong><\/p><p><strong><a href=\"#tools\">7 Price Optimization Tools That Drive Sales Lift<\/a><\/strong><\/p><ul><li><a href=\"#wappier\">#1: wappier<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"#competera\">#2: Competera<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"#mage\">#3: Mage<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"#microsoft\">#4: Microsoft Power BI<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"#spy\">#5: Price2Spy<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"#prisync\">#6: Prisync<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"#qualtrics\">#7: Qualtrics<\/a><\/li><\/ul><p><em>Ready to see how wappier\u2019s AI and ML-powered price optimization tools can help your company drive sales lift? <\/em><strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.wappier.com\/lets-talk\"><em>Get in touch<\/em><\/a><em>.<\/em><\/strong><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3bf1ce0 elementor-widget elementor-widget-menu-anchor\" data-id=\"3bf1ce0\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;motion_fx_motion_fx_scrolling&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;,&quot;motion_fx_translateY_effect&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;,&quot;motion_fx_translateY_direction&quot;:&quot;negative&quot;,&quot;motion_fx_translateY_speed&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:4.5,&quot;sizes&quot;:[]},&quot;sticky&quot;:&quot;bottom&quot;,&quot;motion_fx_translateY_affectedRange&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;%&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;sizes&quot;:{&quot;start&quot;:0,&quot;end&quot;:100}},&quot;motion_fx_devices&quot;:[&quot;desktop&quot;,&quot;tablet&quot;,&quot;mobile&quot;],&quot;sticky_on&quot;:[&quot;desktop&quot;,&quot;tablet&quot;,&quot;mobile&quot;],&quot;sticky_offset&quot;:0,&quot;sticky_effects_offset&quot;:0}\" data-widget_type=\"menu-anchor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"sales\" class=\"elementor-menu-anchor\"><\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2094047 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"2094047\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<h2><span lang=\"EN\">What Is Sales Lift?<\/span><\/h2>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3363cdf elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"3363cdf\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<p>Sales lift, also known as incremental lift, is a measure of the effectiveness of a company\u2019s promotional pricing, advertising campaigns, or marketing efforts. In order to calculate sales lift, companies compare the incremental increase in sales during a set promotional period to the baseline sales that would have predictably occurred within the same timeframe without the promotion. The difference between actual sales (accomplished during the promotional period) and baseline sales (expected sales without the promotion) equals sales lift.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e18f807 elementor-widget elementor-widget-menu-anchor\" data-id=\"e18f807\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"menu-anchor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"PredictiveAnalyticsVSPredictiveModeling\" class=\"elementor-menu-anchor\"><\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3c01973 elementor-widget elementor-widget-menu-anchor\" data-id=\"3c01973\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"menu-anchor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"lift\" class=\"elementor-menu-anchor\"><\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-bbe5334 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"bbe5334\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<h2><span lang=\"EN\">Why Is Sales Lift Important?<\/span><\/h2>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-dc98e8a elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"dc98e8a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<p>Measuring sales lift is important because it helps organizations understand and prove the impact of their advertising and marketing investments. Crunching the numbers allows companies to see the actual results produced by any given campaign, empowering advertising and marketing leaders to improve their strategies and optimize pricing to yield improved results over time.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b602a31 elementor-widget elementor-widget-menu-anchor\" data-id=\"b602a31\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"menu-anchor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"play\" class=\"elementor-menu-anchor\"><\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ccd8799 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"ccd8799\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<h2><span lang=\"EN\">What Role Does Price Optimization Play In Sales Lift?<\/span><\/h2>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ee70016 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"ee70016\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<p>Although the basic formula is simple, there are countless elements that can contribute to sales lift calculations. One of the most important variables is price, which defines the specific value of each promotional offer or discount. As sales teams begin to analyze lift, pulling the levers of price can help refine promotional strategies and see improved results. That\u2019s because offering consumers the right promotion at the right time can make or break their decision to buy. Instead of stabbing in the dark to pull those levers, companies can use pricing optimization software to make sure they are matching consumers with the perfect promotions to drive lift as high as possible.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b85aed4 elementor-widget elementor-widget-menu-anchor\" data-id=\"b85aed4\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"menu-anchor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"tools\" class=\"elementor-menu-anchor\"><\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-66a9fff elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"66a9fff\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<h2><span lang=\"EN\">7 Price Optimization Tools That Drive Sales Lift<\/span><\/h2>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9f7abba elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"9f7abba\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<p>Let\u2019s look at how seven leading sales analytics and price optimization tools help companies drive lift:<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-de88b35 elementor-widget elementor-widget-menu-anchor\" data-id=\"de88b35\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"menu-anchor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"BlockchainGameExamples\" class=\"elementor-menu-anchor\"><\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9fabe39 elementor-widget elementor-widget-menu-anchor\" data-id=\"9fabe39\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"menu-anchor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"wappier\" class=\"elementor-menu-anchor\"><\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-