likelihood to purchase. Price optimization capabilities like these are how wappier helps mobile developers drive incremental sales lift across all their promotional efforts.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-cc9df1b elementor-widget elementor-widget-menu-anchor\" data-id=\"cc9df1b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"menu-anchor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"competera\" class=\"elementor-menu-anchor\"><\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-11d2ffa elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"11d2ffa\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<h3><span lang=\"EN\">#2: Competera<\/span><\/h3>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3634244 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"3634244\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<p><strong><a href=\"https:\/\/competera.net\/\">Competera<\/a> <\/strong>gives marketers a 360-degree view of their markets with fresh data updated every two hours. Retail and e-commerce brands can build their own rules to drive pricing automations, or lean on demand-based price recommendations and real-time repricing suggestions. With a suite of tools powered by machine learning technology and trained to recognize both price-related and other factors, Competera promises to reduce repricing time by 50%, increase revenue by 8%, and increase profit margin by 6%.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\