ata-id=\"7c9c9cf\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"menu-anchor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"microsoft\" class=\"elementor-menu-anchor\"><\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-638887d elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"638887d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<h3><span lang=\"EN\">#4: Microsoft Power BI<\/span><\/h3>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-31cc634 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"31cc634\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<p><strong><a href=\"https:\/\/powerbi.microsoft.com\/en-us\/\">Microsoft Power BI<\/a> <\/strong>offers companies sales analytics and data visualization tools they can use to better understand their effectiveness and improve their strategies over time. The software\u2019s AI capabilities power a range of pre-built and customizable visualization options that allow advertisers and marketers to analyze lift. By measuring the effectiveness of their efforts from any number of angles and perspectives, companies can use Power BI to anticipate how price optimization will affect those results.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-589dc74 elementor-widget elementor-widget-menu-anchor\" data-id=\"589dc74\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"menu-anchor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"spy\" class=\"elementor-menu-anchor\"><\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3846c1b elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"3846c1b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<h3><span lang=\"EN\">#5: Price2Spy<\/span><\/h3>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6a82be9 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"6a82be9\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<p><strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.price2spy.com\/\">Price2Spy<\/a><\/strong> gives marketers a complete picture of the pricing landscape in their vertical. Real-time competitor pricing comparisons, historical data analysis, and repricing opportunity alerts help marketers optimize to stay in peak profitability. With various tiers of service available that unlock increasingly advanced features, Price2Spy is an adaptable price optimization tool that can help online merchants of any size drive lift over time.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-02cc8eb elementor-widget elementor-widget-menu-anchor\" data-id=\"02cc8eb\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"menu-anchor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"prisync\" class=\"elementor-menu-anchor\"><\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f43f035 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"f43f035\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<h3><span lang=\"EN\">#6: Prisync<\/span><\/h3>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8ce9a16 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"8ce9a16\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<p><strong><a href=\"https:\/\/prisync.com\/\">Prisync<\/a> <\/strong>allows marketers to input any number of products they sell and monitor competitor pricing in real time. Robust analytics inform per-category indices and demonstrate historical pricing trends so you can optimize your own brand\u2019s pricing based on what\u2019s occurring in the market. The Prisync system also offers stock availability details, so that brands can track what competitors are selling out of and capitalize on opportunities to fill gaps and meet growing demand.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5480d14 elementor-widget elementor-widget-menu-anchor\" data-id=\"5480d14\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"menu-anchor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"qualtrics\" class=\"elementor-menu-anchor\"><\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3bef08e elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"3bef08e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<h3><span lang=\"EN\">#7: Qualtrics<\/span><\/h3>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a664e44 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"a664e44\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<p><strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.qualtrics.com\/product-experience\/pricing-research-software\/\">Qualtrics<\/a>\u2019<\/strong> price optimization software allows companies to consolidate all their pricing research in one place. Industry-leading studies like the Van Westendrop price sensitivity meter and Gabor-Granger analysis provide a basis from which brands can understand their place in the existing market. With data visualization capabilities and complex logic tools, Qualtrics promises to make it easy for companies to compare themselves against competitors and find the optimal pricing that will allow them to drive lift.<\/p><p>Price optimization tools help companies drive sales lift by ensuring that each consumer sees the right promotional pricing at the right time. wappier uses AI and machine learning technology to power our price optimization products and help mobile game companies improve critical metrics like in-app revenue, customer lifetime value, and more. Ready to learn more about how wappier can help your company optimize pricing to drive sales lift?<strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.wappier.com\/lets-talk\">Contact us today.<\/a><\/strong><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>When it comes to performance metrics, incremental lift is often considered by many to be the key to the kingdom. The ability to prove the effectiveness of a specific promotion can earn marketing and advertising teams access to i